==English==
===Etymology===
From the practice of substituting a cat etc for a suckling pig when sold in a sack at a market
===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[pig]] in a [[poke]]'''
#{{idiom}}  something [[given]] in a manner such that its [[true]] [[value]] is [[concealed]]
